org.gephi.graph.api
Interface Renderable

All Superinterfaces:
Spatial
All Known Subinterfaces:
EdgeData, NodeData
All Known Implementing Classes:
EdgeDataImpl, NodeDataImpl
public interface Renderable
extends Spatial

All graphic attributes a renderable element can have. Renderable elements are elements such as nodes and edges.

Author:
Mathieu Bastian
